text: John McInnes (born 7 July 1939) is a Canadian ski jumper. He competed at the 1964 Winter Olympics and the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Canada Category:Ski jumpers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:Ski jumpers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from New Westminster
